Map Layers Guide

  • Dominant Tier: Circles color-coded by main price tier in locality
  • Avg Cost: Circles color-coded from blue (lowest) to red (highest) cost
  • Avg Rating: Circles color-coded from red (lowest) to green (highest) rating
  • Restaurant Clusters: DBSCAN clusters with circle at centroid
  • Affordable Spots Heatmap: ≤ ₹500
  • Premium Spots Heatmap: > ₹1200

Circle size = # of restaurants in the locality.

Open Layer Control (top-right) to toggle each layer on/off.
